keyMappings:
unmapAll

map I enterInsertMode

map ` LinkHints.activateMode
map ~ LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab

map j scrollDown
map k scrollUp
map h scrollLeft
map l scrollRight

map gg scrollToTop
map G  scrollToBottom
map g$ scrollToLeft
map g0 scrollToRight

map [[ goPrevious
map ]] goNext

map gi focusInput
map gf nextFrame
map gF mainFrame

map g- goBack
map g+ goForward
map gT previousTab
map gt nextTab

map <C-/> enterFindMode
map <C-n> performFind
map <C-N> performBackwardsFind
